data.description: Don't miss this beautiful home located in the desirable Cooley Station area in Gilbert. Featuring over 1800 sqft the floor plan offers 3 bedrooms, 3 baths & upstairs Loft. Main floor is open & provides separate living areas for living, family & dining rooms. Even a bedroom & bath on the main floor. Kitchen is upgraded and a solar panel system on roof for more affordable utilities. Other amenities; 18 in tile, upgraded lighting package, hardware & fixtures, ceiling fans & window coverings, large walk in master closet, & storage spaces. Great curb appeal, Natural lighting throughout, Laundry room conveniently located upstairs, 2 car garage, & more! Community pool and gorgeous parks are within walking distance. Location is everything, close to schools, mall, and freeways. Come see it today
